SENATE BILL 194
Q1, C8, P1 6lr0616
(PRE–FILED)
By: Senator Simonaire Senators Simonaire, Bailey, Corderman, McKay,
Rosapepe, and Salling
Requested: June 27, 2025
Introduced and read first time: January 14, 2026
Assigned to: Budget and Taxation
Committee Report: Favorable with amendments
Senate action: Adopted
Read second time: February 15, 2026
CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Income and Property Tax Incentives – Members and Veterans of the Space
3 Force – Application
4 FOR the purpose of applying certain provisions of law relating to the job creation tax credit
5 and certain property tax credits and exemptions for certain members, veterans, and
6 surviving spouses of certain members and veterans of the military, naval, or air
7 service to certain members, veterans, and surviving spouses of certain members and
8 veterans of the space force; and generally relating to income and property tax
9 incentives for members, veterans, and surviving spouses of members and veterans
10 of the space force.
11 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
12 Article – State Government
13 Section 9–901
14 Annotated Code of Maryland
15 (2021 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
16 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
17 Article – Economic Development
18 Section 6–301(a)
19 Annotated Code of Maryland
20 (2024 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
